16/6773596/image8.png' width='236' height='196' /></p><p><img src='https://file.xinjiaoyu.com/prod/question/image/20230116/6773597/image9.png' width='165' height='126' /></p><p>注：<i>bgaB</i>基因表达的&beta;-半乳糖苷酶可以将化合物X－gal转化为蓝色物质，从而使菌落由白色变为蓝色；<i>Cm</i><sup>R</sup>表示氯霉素抗性基因。</p><p>(1)枯草芽孢杆菌的基因组DNA使用限制酶<i>Sau</i>3AⅠ切割后，产生的末端可写为_________。<i>pS</i>Ⅰ质粒使用<i>Bam</i>HⅠ切割后，能与枯草芽孢杆菌的DNA片段成功连接的原因是__________________________________________________________________________。</p><p>(2)据图分析，为达到筛选强启动子的目的，需要对<i>bgaB</i>基因进行的改造是_____________。<i>Cm</i><sup>R</sup>基因的作用是__________________________________________________________。</p><p>(3)转化后的大肠杆菌需接种在含________的培养基中培养，一段时间后，选择______色的菌落作为目的菌落。</p><p>(4)科研人员分别挑取目的菌落进行培养后，测得含有枯草芽孢杆菌某DNA片段的大肠杆菌中&beta;-半乳糖苷酶含量明显增多，说明__________________________________________。</p>","createBy":"36003","createName":null,"createTime":"2023-01-16T10:22:56","decipherment":null,"deleted":false,"difficultyId":"10019","difficultyName":"中档题","gradeId":null,"id":"821569265818671110","isCharged":false,"isGroupQuestion":false,"isSubjective":true,"lineNumber":1,"oldId":null,"optionA":null,"optionB":null,"optionC":null,"optionD":null,"optionE":null,"optionF":null,"optionG":null,"options":[],"origin":1,"paperTypeId":null,"parentId":"0","pickCount":0,"provinceId":null,"questionNumber":null,"questionSerialNo":3541496,"questionVideo":null,"relateKnowledge":null,"scoreBasis":null,"source":null,"title":null,"typeDetailId":"6","typeDetailName":"简答题","typeId":"67","typeName":"非选择题","updateBy":"36003","updateName":null,"updateTime":"2023-01-16T10:22:56","uploadBatch":"1673835776984","yearId":null},"questionId":"821569265818671110","questionNumber":"16"}],"title":""}],"templateId":"177772","templateName":"第3章（3）　第2节　第2课时　将目的基因导入受体细胞、目的基因的检测与鉴定"},"msg":null}